		<DIV ALIGN="CENTER"><FONT SIZE="+2">Elemental Power</FONT><BR>
Zone : Temple of Solusek Ro<BR><BR>
<TABLE CELLSPACING = 0 CELLPADDING = 0 BORDER = 0>
<TR><TD><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="ariel"><B>Added:</B>February 27th 2000</B><BR><BR>

Vira will construct four mage items which, when wielded while summoning the pet of the element the item represents above level 34 (the level limit seems to not work, and the items seem to affect the stats of any summoned pet for now), will significantly boost the power the pet.  They are also decent 1HB weapons.  You need to fetch him the proper ingredients to make the item. <BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/weapon_detail.php3?search=341">Torch of Alna:</A> [Fire Elemental] A Fire Emerald, A Scale from a Fire Drake, A Torch (from a Magician in Najena or alligator in Cazic) and the toes of a Fire Giant.<BR>
<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/weapon_detail.php3?search=330">Broom of Trilon:</A> [Air Elemental]  A Star Ruby, A Feather from a Griffon, A Broom (from a Magician in Najena or alligator in Cazic) and the toes of a Cyclops.<BR>
<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/weapon_detail.php3?search=342">Stein of Ulissa:</A> [Water Elemental] A Sapphire, A Scale from a Mermaid, A Stein (from a Magician in Najena or alligator in Cazic) and the toes of a Frost Giant.<BR>
<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/weapon_detail.php3?search=333">Shovel of Ponz:</A> [Earth Elemental]  A Ruby, The Eyes of a Gargoyle, A Shovel (from a Magician in Najena or alligator in Cazic) and the toes of a Hill Giant.<BR><BR>
</TD></TR>
